metadata.name: DOS TRASH BIRD 330
metadata.description: Not affiliated with Proof Collective or Moonbirds. DOS Trash Birds is a 1k collection by Empress Trash and Max Capacity. Hand curated from ~13k dossified generations of Original Moonbirds this collection is a bonafide cash grab for fun, the art and to celebrate CC0 remix culture. 20% of all sales primary and secondary goes to DOS Punks Dao to support new and emerging artists.
